Package com.github.tommyettinger.gdcrux

Class PointI6

java.lang.Object
com.github.tommyettinger.gdcrux.PointI6
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Json.Serializable, com.github.tommyettinger.crux.Point6<PointI6>, com.github.tommyettinger.crux.PointN<PointI6>, Externalizable, Serializable
public class PointI6 extends Object implements com.github.tommyettinger.crux.Point6<PointI6>, com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Json.Serializable, Externalizable
If GridPoint6 existed, this would be like it, just implementing Point6, Json.Serializable, and Externalizable. This does have some more additions to those interfaces, such as get(int) and setAt(int, int).
